{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What happened to Kamilia?</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654030/extras/About_A2.jpg?t=1736533501\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Kamilia is a unique detective mystery, that follows the story of a talented painter, as he finds himself involved in an ongoing murder investigation that was left unsolved for years.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654030/extras/About_B2.jpg?t=1736533501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In 1909, a dramatic event shook the entire town of Roga and started a chain of events that led to an unsolvable crime.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">8 years later, it is up to you to learn the truth, and clear the unsettling shadows of death that took over Roga.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654030/extras/About_D2.jpg?t=1736533501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Throughout the game, you will play as multiple characters, and make important choices that will shape the outcome of the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654030/extras/About_C.jpg?t=1736533501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Immerse yourself in an intense and emotional story, as the painter struggles to unveil the town's secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2654030/extras/About_E.jpg?t=1736533501\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key features </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Unique story-rich visual novel, with moderate puzzle eleme